; bringup.tscn — toolchain proof. Rig + one grabbable cube,
; NO game code. Deploy THIS to the Quest first to prove OpenXR + rig + grab + export/deploy
; work, before debugging any game logic. "Never debug your code and the toolchain together."
; Temporarily set run/main_scene to res://bringup.tscn (or run this scene with F6) to check it.
; ⚠️ Open in Godot 4.7 once to assign UIDs + confirm the addon resolves.
[gd_scene load_steps=5 format=3]

